### PageRuntime 运行态页面接口

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!
@appKey = crm_demo_2026
@pageKey = customer-form

### 登录获取令牌
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 获取 Anti-Forgery Token
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### 获取运行态已发布页面 Schema（按 appKey/pageKey）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runtime/apps/{{appKey}}/pages/{{pageKey}}/schema
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 运行态表单提交（简化对象载荷）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runtime/apps/{{appKey}}/pages/{{pageKey}}/records
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "运行态用户A",
  "email": "runtime-user-a@example.com",
  "mobile": "13800000000",
  "isActive": true
}

### 运行态表单提交（标准 values 载荷）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runtime/apps/{{appKey}}/pages/{{pageKey}}/records
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "values": [
    {
      "field": "name",
      "valueType": "String",
      "stringValue": "运行态用户B"
    },
    {
      "field": "isActive",
      "valueType": "Bool",
      "boolValue": true
    }
  ]
}

### 获取运行态页面元信息（RuntimeRoute）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runtime/apps/{{appKey}}/pages/{{pageKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取运行态菜单（已发布页面自动注册）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runtime/apps/{{appKey}}/menu
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取当前用户运行态待办任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runtime/tasks?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 执行运行态任务动作（approve/reject/transfer/delegate）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runtime/tasks/1/actions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "approve",
  "comment": "runtime approve test"
}

### 草稿态页面访问校验（应返回 404/业务失败）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runtime/apps/{{appKey}}/pages/draft-only-page/schema
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [兼容窗口检查] v1 runtime 入口（应返回迁移提示）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runtime/tasks?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [迁移契约占位] v2 runtime-contexts 目标路径（未落地前可能返回 404/501）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-contexts?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [迁移契约占位] v2 runtime-executions 目标路径（未落地前可能返回 404/501）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/runtime-executions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
